        "All repositories must use the shared workflow templates in the .github/workflows directory of the platform-configs repository. Custom workflows require Platform Engineering team approval. Workflow runs are limited to 60 minutes; long-running jobs must be split into parallel stages. Self-hosted runners are available for builds requiring GPU access or specialized hardware.\n",
