        "ACME maintains four environments: development (auto-deployed on PR creation), staging (deployed on merge to main), canary (5% production traffic), and production. Environment variables and secrets are managed through HashiCorp Vault. Each environment has isolated database instances — production data never flows to non-production environments.\n",
